2002;;Path to War;;American;;John Frankenheimer;;Michael Gambon, Alec Baldwin, Donald Sutherland, Felicity Huffman, Tom Skerritt, Frederic Forrest, Diana Scarwid;;drama, biography;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Path_to_War;;The film deals directly with the Vietnam War as seen through the eyes of United States President Lyndon B. Johnson and his cabinet members. The starting events portrayed begin in 1965.